## Input Actions Configuration
## This file documents all input actions used in the fighting game
## Can be added to project.godot or registered at runtime via InputManager._register_input_actions()

class_name InputActions

# Player 1 Controls (WASD + JKL)
# p1_left: A key - Move left
# p1_right: D key - Move right
# p1_up: W key - Move up
# p1_down: S key - Move down
# p1_attack: J key - Basic attack
# p1_special: K key - Special move

# Player 2 Controls (Arrow Keys + Numpad)
# p2_left: Left Arrow - Move left
# p2_right: Right Arrow - Move right
# p2_up: Up Arrow - Move up
# p2_down: Down Arrow - Move down
# p2_attack: Numpad 1 - Basic attack
# p2_special: Numpad 2 - Special move

